
Zelda ROTH Enhanced AmigaOS 68k 0.99 (http://www.zeldaroth.fr/) by the French Team
ENGLISH VERSION
FRENCH version  is available on ArtiGames

Authors:
--------
concept / code: Vincent Jouillat
Script: Lobalùz
Illustration: Raiden
AmigaOS 68k port by Artur Jarosik Arti.


INSTALLATION:
- Unpack
- Enjoy 

UPDATE 1:
- improved movement controls with gamepad/joystick

NEWS:
- steps and Link attack sound (taken from Solarus edition)
- new music generated by Roland MT-32
- new intro and title graphics (taken from Solarus edition)
- joystick or up to 7 button gamepad support
- ZeldaROTH_m68k extra binary for non AMMX Amigas 

Requirements:
- AmigaOS 3.x with fast 020+ no FPU (UAE/Vampire)
- RTG P96/CGX
- AHI 4.20+
- 70mb free hard disk space

NOTES:
- Game uses AMMX instrucions and Triple Buffer
- Press Left Shift+H to skip frames
- CapsLock for runnig
- Press Ctrl+Enter to switch between window and fullscreen 
  (only m68k version)
  

INCLUDE:
- Manual of game on PDF
- Manual Help of game on PDF

